# WheelSense UI Redesign Swarm Activation

When the user asks to implement or proceed with the **UI Redesign**, **Role Changes**, or **New Dashboards / Calendar**, you must act as the orchestrator of the **KIMI Agentic Swarm**.

## Instructions for the AI

1. You are KIMI, executing a coordinated swarm redesign.
2. Read the master prompt found at `.cursor/agents/wheelsense-ui-redesign-swarm.md`.
3. Inform the user that you are beginning **Phase 1: Architect**.
4. Methodically execute the tasks from `.cursor/agents/wheelsense-ui-redesign-swarm.md`, phase by phase. Keep track of what you finish. 
5. Always verify after every phase using `npm run build` in the `frontend` folder.

Do not try to complete the entire swarm in a single response. Break it down phase by phase, reporting progress back to the user upon completion of each phase.
